      <title>大风可能在休斯顿附近散布野火火焰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-21/high-winds-could-spread-flames-of-wildfire-near-houston-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州的几个野火燃烧，包括圣哈辛托县山姆·休斯顿国家森林的波琳路大火。有强制性撤离，燃烧了2300多英亩。预计大风将散布火焰。整个地区的火灾风险升高。  （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-21/high-winds-could-spread-flames-of-wildfire-near-houston-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 15:14:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
